Package appServices

This package contains classes related to system back-end and operations between database, booking and admin
Author:
Mohamed Reda-Elbaz 20190440, Ahmed Mohamed Ahmed 20190060
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Booking
    Booking class contains all activated playgrounds, book a playground, send booking requests for players and playground owners
    Database
    Database class contains all users information of registered users
    Main
    Main class show main screen(registration page)
    Requests
    Class Requests is responsible for playground reservation in specific slot
    SystemUI
    Class SystemUI is responsible for interaction between users and other system
